## Command Options Summary

| Option | Short | Description | Default |
| ------ | ----- | ----------- | ------- |
| `--filter` | `-f` | Filter books by title (case-insensitive) | None |
| `--details` | `-d` | Show detailed table view | False |
| `--sort` | `-s` | Sort field: title, size, date, pages | title |
| `--reverse` | `-r` | Descending sort order | False |
